                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-223-18361128 t18361128-223-punishment-206"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">First Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
